This is an open-source rhetoric handbook project.

Principal authors: Kathleen Vandenberg and Alan Taylor.

INSTRUCTIONS:

1. Choose the chapters that you would like to include in your personalized 
handbook from the Chapters folder. 

2. Edit the Handbook.tex file's \input lines to change the order of chapters or 
remove chapters completely from your personalized handbook.  

3. Use a LaTex editor with the Memoir Class to create a .pdf of your handbook.

CONTRIBUTE:

If you would like to contribute, create a fork of the project.
